ntality:_tribe_mentality,trick_riding:_trick_riding,trick_shooter:_trick_shooter,trick_spell:_trick_spell,triple_baron:_triple_baron,tripping_staff:_tripping_staff,tripping_strike:_tripping_strike,tripping_twirl:_tripping_twirl,triton_portal:_triton_portal,troth_of_the_forgotten_pharaoh:_troth_of_the_forgotten_pharaoh,true_breed:_true_breed,true_deception:_true_deception,true_love:_true_love,truth_in_wine:_truth_in_wine,truth_seeker:_truth_seeker,tumbling_upset:_tumbling_upset,tumultuous_spell:_tumultuous_spell,tundra_stride:_tundra_stride,tunnel_rat:_tunnel_rat,turbulent_takeoff:_turbulent_takeoff,turn_undead:_turn_undead,twilight_tattoo:_twilight_tattoo,twilight_words:_twilight_words,twin_fang_lunge:_twin_fang_lunge,twin_fang_strike:_twin_fang_strike,twin_fang_style:_twin_fang_style,twin_thunders:_twin_thunders,twin_thunders_flurry:_twin_thunders_flurry,twin_thunders_master:_twin_thunders_master,twinned_feint:_twinned_feint,twist_away:_twist_away,twisted_love:_twisted_love,two_fisted_drinker:_two_fisted_drinker,two_handed_thrower:_two_handed_thrower,two_weapon_defense:_two_weapon_defense,two_weapon_drunkard:_two_weapon_drunkard,two_weapon_feint:_two_weapon_feint,two_weapon_fighting:_two_weapon_fighting,two_weapon_grace:_two_weapon_grace,two_weapon_rend:_two_weapon_rend,tyrants_rebuke:_tyrants_rebuke,ultimate_mercy:_ultimate_mercy,ultimate_resolve:_ultimate_resolve,umbral_scion:_umbral_scion,umbral_shift:_umbral_shift,umbral_spell:_umbral_spell,unaging:_unaging,unbalancing_blow:_unbalancing_blow,unblinking_flame_feint:_unblinking_flame_feint,unblinking_flame_fist:_unblinking_flame_fist,unbound_bravery:_unbound_bravery,unbreakable:_unbreakable,uncanny_activation:_uncanny_activation,uncanny_alertness:_uncanny_alertness,uncanny_ally:_uncanny_ally,uncanny_concentration:_uncanny_concentration,uncanny_defense:_uncanny_defense,uncertainty:_uncertainty,uncivilized_tactics:_uncivilized_tactics,unconquerable_resolve:_unconquerable_resolve,undaunted_bravery:_undaunted_bravery